venueDescription: BRICKLANE (Admiralty), with its spacious and versatile layout complete with a huge terrace that oversees the Victoria Harbour, offers scenic alfresco dining experience to compliment every occasion. Apart from being one of the best places to view festive fireworks display in Hong Kong, it is an ideal location for weddings, private parties, corporate functions, fashion shows, business seminars and more.
Really good place to work and have an event space
